Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:05.32,TranslationED,,0,0,0,,When you're lost and alone, \Ncall out and lead me to your side
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.94,0:00:10.83,TranslationED,,0,0,0,,As you wander far from home, \Nyou search the sky and never hide
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.06,0:00:13.74,TranslationED,,0,0,0,,You are so much like the moon
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.81,0:00:18.19,TranslationED,,0,0,0,,Calmer than a star, your twinkling's lost
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.04,0:00:30.59,TranslationED,,0,0,0,,A deep reflection shines, you slowly leave, \Nfading, and what's the cost?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.05,0:00:35.88,TranslationED,,0,0,0,,Stay as you are, don't lose your way
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.17,0:00:44.13,TranslationED,,0,0,0,,Let my words guide you, \Nand look ahead until the day!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.17,0:00:51.04,TranslationED,,0,0,0,,Don't give up on your dreams, \Nthrough endless nights they come to you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.41,0:00:56.64,TranslationED,,0,0,0,,If you stop, you'll never see them shining through!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.28,0:01:02.61,TranslationED,,0,0,0,,Will you return? Maybe not... \NWill you learn? I hope you do
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.61,0:01:08.80,TranslationED,,0,0,0,,Please put your past to rest, \Nand live your life anew.
